libs.content:
find_library(_tbb_lib names tbb
        hints "${tbbroot}"
        path_suffixes lib lib64)
find_program(lintian_program names lintian doc "path to lintian tool")
find_program(rpmlint_program names rpmlint doc "path to rpmlint tool")

deps.context: find_package(opencv quiet components gapi core imgproc)

find_package(libgna required
             config
             paths "${cmake_current_source_dir}/cmake"
             no_default_path
             no_cmake_find_root_path)

find_package( cython required
              paths "${cmake_current_source_dir}/cmake"
              no_cmake_find_root_path
              no_default_path )

libs.content: find_program(fdupes_program names fdupes doc "path to fdupes")

deps.context: find_package(openvino required components runtime optional_components onnx)
find_package(onnx 1.13.1 exact quiet components onnx onnx_proto no_module)

libs.content: find_library(pugixml_library names pugixml doc "path to pugixml library")

deps.context: find_package(opencv quiet components core imgproc imgcodecs)
find_package(opencv quiet components core imgproc imgcodecs)
